org.bremersee.dccon.repository.cli

Interface DhcpLeaseParser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommandExecutorResponseParser<List<org.bremersee.dccon.model.DhcpLease>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DhcpLeaseParser.Default

    public interface DhcpLeaseParser
extends CommandExecutorResponseParser<List<org.bremersee.dccon.model.DhcpLease>>
    The dhcp lease list parser parses the response of the linux command line tool dhcp-lease-list.

    A response of dhcp-lease-list looks like this: 

     MAC b8:xx:xx:xx:xx:xx IP 192.168.1.109 HOSTNAME ukelei BEGIN 2019-08-18 11:20:33 END 2019-08-18 11:50:33 MANUFACTURER Apple, Inc.
 MAC ac:xx:xx:xx:xx:yy IP 192.168.1.188 HOSTNAME -NA- BEGIN 2019-08-18 11:25:48 END 2019-08-18 11:55:48 MANUFACTURER Super Micro Computer, Inc.
    Author:
    Christian Bremer
